HW3 Problem 2: Static Priority Scheduling

This program implements static priority scheduling using SCHED_FIFO on Linux.

Build:
make -f Makefile2

Run:
./rtsched -static <input_file>

The input file should contain lines of period execution deadline, in priority order (highest first).

The program generates gantt.dat and static.png for the Gantt chart.

Note: Run on ARC cluster for correct real-time behavior.